  "title": "Namespace Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections",
  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections' data-commentId='N:Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Collections'>Namespace Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections   </h1>\r\n <h3 class='section'>Classes</h3><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.EnumerableHelpers.html'>EnumerableHelpers</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Internal helper functions for working with enumerables.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.FastestArrayPool-1.html'>FastestArrayPool&lt;T&gt;</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The fastest array pool class</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.IdTable.html'>IdTable</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The id table class</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.IdTable-1.html'>IdTable&lt;T&gt;</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The id table class</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.ShortSparseSet-1.html'>ShortSparseSet&lt;T&gt;</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The short sparse set class</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.SparseSet-1.html'>SparseSet&lt;T&gt;</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The sparse set class</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section'>Structs</h3><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.ArchetypeNeighborCache.html'>ArchetypeNeighborCache</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">A 4-way set-associative cache mapping source archetype IDs to destination archetypes.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.Chunk-1.html'>Chunk&lt;TData&gt;</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The chunk</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.FastestStack-1.Enumerator.html'>FastestStack&lt;T&gt;.Enumerator</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The enumerator</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.FastLookup.html'>FastLookup</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The fast lookup</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.FastestStack-1.html'>FastestStack&lt;T&gt;</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The fastest stack class</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.FastestTable-1.html'>FastestTable&lt;T&gt;</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The fastest table combining optimal performance traits, safe version.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.FrugalStack-1.html'>FrugalStack&lt;T&gt;</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The frugal stack</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.InlineArray8-1.html'>InlineArray8&lt;T&gt;</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Collections.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The inline array</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
